Package jibe.sdk.client.events

Event subscription model used by the Jibe SDK to notify a client application of changes in state see Connection lifecyle

See:
          Description

Class Summary
JibeEvent Base class for all Jibe Service events.
JibeEvent.Category Available event categories.
JibeEventIms JibeEvent class for IMS and RCS-e events, such as capability-discovery, user-discovery, and bootstrap configuration.
JibeEventObserver Abstract base class, used to implement observers for the event mechanism.
JibeEventRcsConfig JibeEvent subclass, which deals specifically with RCS-e config-related events.
JibeEventService Allows client applications to manage their subscription to specific categories of events.
JibeSessionEvent The Jibe Event class for session events.
 

Package jibe.sdk.client.events Description

Event subscription model used by the Jibe SDK to notify a client application of changes in state see Connection lifecyle
